+    // ── legacy +freeq.at/multiline \\n normalization ──────────────────────────
+
+    /// PRIVMSG bearing the legacy `+freeq.at/multiline` tag must have its
+    /// literal `\n` escape sequences (two chars: backslash + n) replaced with
